                        <h4 class="title"> Stroke Disease Detection</h4>
                    </a>
                    <p class="description">
                        Early detection and appropriate management are required to prevent
                        further damage to the affected area of the brain and other
                        complications in other parts of the body.
                    </p>
                </div>


